PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the CONVENTION ON CLUSTER MUNITIONS negotiated in Dublin in May 2008 and opened for signature in Oslo, on December 3, 2008. The purpose of this Convention is to address the unacceptable harm caused to civilian populations by cluster munitions.
